name: WaveSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open wave sounds”
”Alexa ask wave sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wave sounds
des: Pretend you are falling asleep at ocean's edge with these breaking wave sounds! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Wave Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
